                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. Several separation techniques such as ion",
                "exchange chromatography, solid phase extraction, liquid",
                "liquid extraction and co-precipitation have been",
                "investigated to separate no-carrier-added",
                "radiomanganese from the bulk target chromium. For",
                "production purposes, a sandwiched pellet of the",
                "chemical composition Al(4)Cr-50-Cl(3) was developed as",
                "a new target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "2GERJUL"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The compact cyclotron CV-28."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC",
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A beam current of 3-muA was applied for 1-hr."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Isotopically enriched Cr-50 in metallic form was",
                "used, the isotopic composition of was",
                "Cr-50 -94.7+-0.4%,",
                "Cr-52 -4.84%,",
                "Cr-53 -0.37%,",
                "Cr-54 -0.09%.",
                "The chemical impurities (in ppm)",
                "supplier, were- Ti  less 30, Mn  less 10, Fe less 250,",
                "Ni less 40, Cu - 80, Al -780, Si -200 and Ca -150.",
                "The Al(4)Cr-50Cl(3) pellet was made by pressing a",
                "mixture of 70-mg Cr-50Cl(3) and 50-mg Al powder between",
                "two polyethylene foils in a pellet press. The pellet",
                "thus contained 20-mg of Cr-50."
              ]
            }
          ],
